channel.description:
[IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/fp3y2e.jpg[/img]
Base: Delta
Hello all this is my first server and It might not be much but is it what I can do. While the server is up I will be making updates but right now it's complete and I wish to release it. This server will not have any new items such as d claws, vestas, chaotic. I removed those because I want to bring back the days when rsps was about 3rd age, master wand, and c bow.
